fields.name: ðŸš“ Basic Moderation ðŸš“
fields.value:
`e-ban <@user> <reason>` - Bans a member from the server.
`e-kick <@user>` - Kicks a user from the server.
`e-mute <@user>` - Mutes a user in the server.
`e-unmute <@user>` - Unmutes a user in the server.
`e-invite` - Generates the invite link for the bot.
`e-say <message>` - Broadcasts a message in the channel.
`e-addrole <@user> <role>` - Adds a role to a User.
`e-removerole <@user> <role>` - Removes a role from a User
`e-softban <@user> <reason>` - Soft bans a user from the server.
`e-ping` - Gets the ping of the server and bot.
`e-help` - Displays all the commands of the server.
`e-suggest <suggestion>` - Logs a suggestion to the server.
`e-status` - Changes the status of the bot.
`e-warn <@user>` - Warns a user.
`e-warnings <@user>` - Displays all the past warnings of a user.
`e-clearwarnings <@user>` - Clears all the warnings of a user.
